    { question: "Which appraisal approach is most reliable for single-family homes?", options: ["Cost approach", "Sales comparison approach", "Income approach", "Gross rent multiplier"], answer: 1, explanation: "The sales comparison approach is most reliable for residential property with many recent comparable sales." },
